"attendant.protocol.violentIndividual.step3" = "If the person persists in being disruptive, ask him to leave and inform the attendant overseer immediately.";
"attendant.protocol.violentIndividual.step4" = "If the individual refuses to leave, inform him that the police will be contacted.";
"attendant.protocol.violentIndividual.step5" = "If the individual becomes violent, see the Avoid / Deny / Defend protocol for an active shooter situation.";

